Package: ggbuilder
Title: An alternative way to build ggplot2 layers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew", "Kay", , "mjskay@northwestern.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An (experimental) alternative way to build ggplot2 layers, where elements
    of the layer, such as data, mappings, statistical transformations, and geometries
    are specified in the order their data is processed.
Depends:
  R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
  ggplot2,
  rlang
Suggests:
  dplyr,
  tidyr,
  generics,
  vdiffr,
  testthat (>= 3.0.0)
